<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI智能开发服务 - AI帮你写代码·建网站·做小程序</title>
<meta name="description" content="AI Agent自助开发服务，7×24小时自动接单，按需付费。网站开发、小程序开发、App开发、AI工具定制、PPT设计、文案代写。">
<style>
/* ===== Reset & Base ===== */
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; }
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
  background: #0a0a1a;
  color: #e0e0f0;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ===== Scrollbar ===== */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0a0a1a; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #4a3aff; border-radius: 3px; }

/* ===== Background Particles ===== */
#particles-canvas {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
  z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
}

/* ===== Navigation ===== */
.nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  padding: 16px 24px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  transition: background 0.3s, backdrop-filter 0.3s;
}
.nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(10, 10, 26, 0.85);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 58, 255, 0.2);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
.nav-links a {
  color: #b0b0d0; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: color 0.3s; position: relative;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }
.nav-links a::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0;
  width: 0; height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  transition: width 0.3s;
}
.nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

/* Mobile menu */
.nav-toggle { display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; }
.nav-toggle span { display: block; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: #e0e0f0; margin: 5px 0; transition: 0.3s; }

/* ===== Section Common ===== */
.section {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 100px 24px;
}
.section-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #6c5ce7;
  background: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.12);
  padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #b0b0d0);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
.section-desc { color: #8888aa; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 48px; }

/* ===== Hero ===== */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  padding: 120px 24px 80px;
}
.hero-content { max-width: 800px; }
.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.3);
  padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 30px;
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: #a78bfa;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease;
}
.hero-badge .dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: #00d2ff;
  animation: pulse-dot 2s infinite;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.15s both;
}
.hero h1 .gradient-text {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff, #6c5ce7);
  background-size: 200% auto;
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  animation: gradient-shift 4s ease infinite;
}
.hero p {
  font-size: 1.2rem; color: #8888aa;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.3s both;
}
.hero-buttons {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.45s both;
}
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 12px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #4a3aff);
  color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
  border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
  transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4);
}
.btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.6); }
.btn-secondary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  color: #e0e0f0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
  cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }

/* Hero stats */
.hero-stats {
  display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 48px; margin-top: 64px;
  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.6s both;
}
.hero-stat { text-align: center; }
.hero-stat .num {
  font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
.hero-stat .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6a6a8a; margin-top: 4px; }

/* ===== Services ===== */
.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}
.service-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 36px 28px;
  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, opacity 0.6s;
}
.service-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.service-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
}
.service-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-6px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.15);
  border-color: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.3);
}
.service-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.service-icon {
  width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,92,231,0.15), rgba(0,210,255,0.1));
}
.service-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.service-card p { color: #7a7a9a; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.service-price {
  font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
.service-price span { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400; }

/* ===== Process ===== */
.process-steps {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 16px;
  position: relative;
}
.process-step {
  flex: 1; min-width: 180px; max-width: 220px;
  text-align: center; padding: 28px 16px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s, transform 0.5s, border-color 0.3s;
}
.process-step.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.process-step:hover { border-color: rgba(108,92,231,0.3); }
.step-num {
  width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #4a3aff);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem; color: #fff;
  margin: 0 auto 16px;
}
.process-step h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.process-step p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #7a7a9a; }
.step-arrow {
  display: flex; align-items: center; color: #4a3aff;
  font-size: 1.4rem; padding-top: 10px;
}

/* ===== Payment ===== */
.payment-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}
.payment-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 32px; text-align: center;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s, transform 0.5s, border-color 0.3s;
}
.payment-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.payment-card:hover { border-color: rgba(108,92,231,0.3); }
.payment-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.payment-card .pay-info { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #7a7a9a; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.qr-placeholder {
  width: 180px; height: 180px; margin: 0 auto 16px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: #5a5a7a;
  border: 2px dashed rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.3);
  background: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.05);
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}
.qr-placeholder:hover { border-color: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.6); }
.pay-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #5a5a7a; }

/* ===== Contact ===== */
.contact-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}
.contact-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 32px; text-align: center;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s, transform 0.5s, border-color 0.3s;
}
.contact-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.contact-card:hover { border-color: rgba(108,92,231,0.3); }
.contact-icon {
  width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0 auto 16px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,92,231,0.15), rgba(0,210,255,0.1));
}
.contact-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.contact-card p { color: #7a7a9a; font-size: 0.9rem; }
.contact-card .value {
  font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}

/* ===== CTA Banner ===== */
.cta-banner {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,92,231,0.15), rgba(0,210,255,0.08));
  border: 1px solid rgba(108,92,231,0.2);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 60px 40px;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 0 24px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
}
.cta-banner h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.cta-banner p { color: #7a7a9a; margin-bottom: 28px; }

/* ===== Footer ===== */
.footer {
  text-align: center; padding: 40px 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  color: #4a4a6a; font-size: 0.82rem;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.footer a { color: #6c5ce7; text-decoration: none; }

/* ===== Animations ===== */
@keyframes fadeInUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes gradient-shift {
  0%, 100% { background-position: 0% center; }
  50% { background-position: 200% center; }
}
@keyframes pulse-dot {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.5); }
}

/* ===== Responsive ===== */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  .nav-links.open {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    position: absolute; top: 60px; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: rgba(10, 10, 26, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    padding: 20px 24px; gap: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(108,92,231,0.2);
  }
  .nav-toggle { display: block; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
  .hero-stat .num { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .process-steps { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .step-arrow { display: none; }
  .section { padding: 60px 16px; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .cta-banner { padding: 40px 20px; }
  .cta-banner h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; }
}

/* ===== Custom Dev Featured Card ===== */
.service-card.featured {
  border-color: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,92,231,0.08), rgba(0,210,255,0.05));
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  position: relative;
}
.service-card.featured::before {
  opacity: 1;
}
.service-card.featured .service-icon {
  width: 64px; height: 64px; font-size: 2rem;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,92,231,0.25), rgba(0,210,255,0.15));
}
.featured-body {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 24px;
}
.featured-info { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }
.featured-info h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.featured-info p { font-size: 1rem; color: #a0a0c0; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.featured-tags {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.featured-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.82rem;
  background: rgba(108,92,231,0.12); color: #a78bfa;
  border: 1px solid rgba(108,92,231,0.2);
}
.featured-price-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.featured-price {
  font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7, #00d2ff);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
.featured-price span { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400; }
.featured-delivery {
  font-size: 0.9rem; color: #00d2ff; font-weight: 600;
}
.btn-cta {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 12px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #ff9a56);
  color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
  border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
  transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(255,107,53,0.4);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255,107,53,0.6); }

/* ===== Business Flow Section ===== */
.biz-flow-steps {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px;
  align-items: center;
}
.biz-flow-step {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  text-align: center; padding: 24px 20px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px; min-width: 140px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}
.biz-flow-step:hover { border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.4); transform: translateY(-4px); }
.biz-flow-step .step-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.biz-flow-step h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.biz-flow-step p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #7a7a9a; }
.biz-flow-arrow {
  font-size: 1.4rem; color: rgba(108,92,231,0.5);
  flex: 0 0 auto;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .biz-flow-steps { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .biz-flow-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .featured-body { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  .featured-tags { justify-content: center; }
  .featured-price-row { justify-content: center; }
  .service-card.featured { grid-column: auto; }
}

/* ===== Contact Modal ===== */
.modal-overlay {
  display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1000;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  justify-content: center; align-items: center;
}
.modal-overlay.active { display: flex; }
.modal-box {
  background: #14142a; border: 1px solid rgba(108,92,231,0.3);
  border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px 36px; max-width: 420px; width: 90%;
  text-align: center; position: relative;
  animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease;
}
.modal-close {
  position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 20px;
  background: none; border: none; color: #7a7a9a; font-size: 1.5rem;
  cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.3s;
}
.modal-close:hover { color: #fff; }
.modal-box h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.modal-box p { color: #7a7a9a; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.modal-contact-item {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.modal-contact-item .micon { font-size: 1.5rem; }
.modal-contact-item .mlabel { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7a7a9a; }
.modal-contact-item .mvalue { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #00d2ff; }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Particles Background -->
<canvas id="particles-canvas"></canvas>

<!-- Navigation -->
<nav class="nav" id="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo">AI<span style="color:#00d2ff">Dev</span> Studio</div>
  <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
    <a href="#tools">免费工具</a><a href="#services">服务项目</a>
    <a href="#biz-flow">商单流程</a>
    <a href="#process">工作流程</a>
    <a href="#payment">收款方式</a>
    <a href="#contact">联系我们</a>
  </div>
  <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="菜单">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </button>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span class="dot"></span> AI Agent 全天候在线接单</div>
    <h1>AI帮你<span class="gradient-text">写代码·建网站·做小程序</span></h1>
    <p>7×24小时自动接单，按需付费，从需求到交付全程AI驱动</p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">立即提交需求</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn-secondary">查看服务项目</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">7×24</div><div class="label">全天在线</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">7+</div><div class="label">服务类别</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">¥29</div><div class="label">起步价</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- Free AI Tools -->
<section class="section" id="tools">
  <div class="section-label">Free Tools</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">免费AI工具</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">即刻体验，无需注册，完全免费</p>
  <div class="free-tools-grid">
    <a href="tools/resume-optimizer/index.html" class="free-tool-card" target="_blank">
      <div class="free-tool-icon">📋</div>
      <h3>AI简历优化器</h3>
      <p>粘贴简历，AI秒出评分+优化建议+优化版简历</p>
      <span class="free-tool-badge">免费使用 →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="tools/ai-copywriter/index.html" class="free-tool-card" target="_blank">
      <div class="free-tool-icon">✍️</div>
      <h3>AI文案生成器</h3>
      <p>小红书/电商/朋友圈/抖音文案，一键生成3个版本</p>
      <span class="free-tool-badge">免费使用 →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="tools/ai-ppt-generator/index.html" class="free-tool-card" target="_blank">
      <div class="free-tool-icon">📊</div>
